So, this video was taken at the airport, and these pictures are just screenshots from it.
While watching it back, I noticed something — my actual expressions kept turning into toned-down versions after just a second.
I’d start with a full, excited face… and then switch to a “prettier,” more controlled one.🌷
Somewhere along the way, I convinced myself that my real energy was “too much.”

Kaafi sad, I know sooo…🤡
I’ve decided I’m going to try to stop doing that 🐷
It won’t change overnight, but being aware of it feels like a good place to start.
And if you’ve ever felt the need to tone yourself down too — I see you. We don’t have to. 🤍

.
.
.
.

.
.

latestPosts.caption:
I wish someone told me this at 20❤️‍🩹
Not every big moment in your life is going to look like the version you imagined.
It might not happen in your dream city, with your favorite people, or in the prettiest setting….
But that doesn’t make it any smaller.
Just because it’s not picture-perfect doesn’t mean it’s not powerful 🎀🐥
Stop shrinking your joy just because it doesn’t “look” the way you thought it would.Okay?❤️
.
.
.
.
.
.
